{"tid":1583877,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"印尼計劃將非婚同居、婚外性行為、同性戀，以及侮辱總統視為犯罪","createTime":"2019-09-21T00:17:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-21T01:25:08.000Z","uid":267131,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"257592b28634423f9c76fbb0a740bfef5dc5a592","tid":1583877,"uid":267131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T00:17:59.000Z","msg":"最近印尼國會有一項刑法草案，計劃將非婚同居、婚外性行為、同性戀，以及侮辱總統視為犯罪，一經發生會被囚禁6個月以及罰款超過一百萬港元。<br />\n<br />\n此草案引起國際社會譁然。而且此草案亦適用於外國遊客，令人擔心遊客會誤墮法網，有機會令人卻步，從而影響印尼旅遊業收入。<br />\n<br />\n人權組織批評草案剝削自由，另擔憂影響言論及新聞自由。組織要求總統介入，否則此草案最快會於下星期通過，影響深遠。<br />\n<br />\n延伸閱讀：<a href=\"https://edition.cnn.com/2019/09/19/asia/indonesia-criminal-code-reform-intl-hnk/index.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fedition.cnn.com%2F2019%2F09%2F19%2Fasia%2Findonesia-criminal-code-reform-intl-hnk%2Findex.html&d=2aT02SOmMwK2whwg3zZG19%2FsvSzfkBtT%2Fd%2Bxj92WHuQ%3D&h=5a50a405\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fedition.cnn.com%2F2019%2F09%2F19%2Fasia%2Findonesia-criminal-code-reform-intl-hnk%2Findex.html&h=68ceef10\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://edition.cnn.com/2019/09/19/asia/indonesia-criminal-code-reform-intl-hnk/index.html</a><br />\n<br />\n(轉載）"},{"pid":"eeccfd9e0db2998e092909bf2b9554fbb016f5fd","tid":1583877,"uid":33930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T00:18:17.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\">由於都係有好多人唔明行動有咩意義同目標 於是係正式攻略之前出個簡化版</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n【行動】【主線】 【922】【SUCK4.0】 【多圖】 【簡易式攻略目標 】<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1583476\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1583476</a>"},{"pid":"575add985412e77bee0e10f20853040dff89b238","tid":1583877,"uid":313514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T00:25:57.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"62015cdd7b86d0f8b9215a3f8570c24422483719","tid":1583877,"uid":313514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"reply